Third Department,

May, 1949.

(May 4, 1949.) In the Matter of the Claim of Mary Johnston, on Behalf of Herself and Others, Respondent, against International Freighting Corp. et al., Appellants, and Nessa Corporation et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.
